  <div class="background-opaque"> 
   <h2 class="fa-3x">Why Ryerson Law</h2> 
   <p>Ryerson’s Faculty of Law has been purpose-built for you, the legal professional of the future. Here, you’ll be equipped with the training and experience required to meet the evolving challenges that face contemporary society as well as the changing demands of the legal economy. From engaging critically with technology as it intersects with the law to exploring new ways to expand the reach of representation and justice, this is a law school designed to help you shape a better future. </p> 
  </div> 
 </div> 
</div>
    
	
