<div class="res-text richtextContent background-opaque" id="2db89db5-11fb-4331-b8f9-d3d86c69e56b" >

    <h3>Diversity &amp; Inclusion</h3> 
<p>It’s imperative that we make the legal profession more diverse as it pertains to backgrounds and perspectives, including Indigenous law. Ryerson Law graduates will be equipped with the multifaceted skills required to serve a broad range of communities, including those who have often been underserved by the legal community.</p>
    





